Title: Frontend Developer
Job Description: Branded Research is a fast-growing, well-capitalized company in the ResTeck space - programmatically delivering millions of consumer insights. We're looking for a front-end engineer to help build and manage our native applications and assist with other front-end development.  In this role, you will help design, build, and maintain scalable mobile products and features that delight millions of Branded community users and help deliver insights. The ideal candidate will be customer-obsessed, highly collaborative, and passionate about creating customer experiences that are both frictionless and delightful. A passion for data science, machine learning, and market research are a plus.
